         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* Mapping macro describing SNAP storage areas list and headers list    00180000
.* The SNAP Plist itself is described in macro's                        00190000
.*     IHASNAP, IHASNAPX, and IHASNP                                    00200000
.*                                                                      00210000
&LABEL   MAPSNAP &DSECT=YES,           * YES or NO                     *00220000
               &CB=,                   * Control block to generate     *00230000
               &PRFX=                  * Prefix to use                  00240000
.********************************************************************** 00241001
.*                                                                      00242001
.*       IMPORTANT NOTICE                                               00243001
.*       ========= ======                                               00244001
